                <h1>Alpine Linux 3.8.1 released</h1>

<p>The Alpine Linux project is pleased to announce the immediate
availability of version 3.8.1 of its Alpine Linux operating system.</p>

<p>This is a bugfix release of the v3.8 stable branch, based on
linux-4.14.69 kernels and it contains bugfixes. It contains an important
security update for apk-tools which <a href="https://git.alpinelinux.org/cgit/apk-tools/commit/?id=6484ed9849f03971eb48ee1fdc21a2f128247eb1">fixes</a> a potential remote execution. A CVE is pending.</p>

<p>The full lists of changes can be found in the <a href="http://git.alpinelinux.org/cgit/aports/log/?h=v3.8.1">git
log</a> and <a href="http://bugs.alpinelinux.org/versions/126">bug
tracker</a>.</p>

